  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Discord!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/6e54d9ace7af485527db96ea9e741a6d.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tower Defense x Roguelite x KOOKY KIDS!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/2fdea31ae2738f9b0b179d95b0ccc646.poster.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/2fdea31ae2738f9b0b179d95b0ccc646.webm?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/2fdea31ae2738f9b0b179d95b0ccc646.mp4?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/f8fb73422adef6960e4bbb6d46362250.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/c538df93db5c0d0b2eef6daeee7828bc.poster.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/c538df93db5c0d0b2eef6daeee7828bc.webm?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/c538df93db5c0d0b2eef6daeee7828bc.mp4?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Spend Munchies to Recruit Base Kids to help defend your Fort and Promote them to Elite Kids!<br></li><li> Place Kids on higher grounds for Range advantage.<br></li><li> Synergize different Kids' unique abilities and damage types to create devastating combinations.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/2404b453e36f574b0a4c4d793e6ab82d.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/6c53bb498018a2fe1a7aeb22229bccdb.poster.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/6c53bb498018a2fe1a7aeb22229bccdb.webm?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/6c53bb498018a2fe1a7aeb22229bccdb.mp4?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Spend Bottle Caps to Use Items on Paths to either set traps, attack Brats directly, or support fellow Kids!<br></li><li> Combine Items' 100% infliction chance of status effects with their associated damage type weakness to deal mega damage.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/547db54ee687f5c629a45f45c6279b39.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/9bb186f2789cf525644a879ebc195256.poster.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/9bb186f2789cf525644a879ebc195256.webm?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/9bb186f2789cf525644a879ebc195256.mp4?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gain randomly generated Perks from clearing Waves, granting new Kids & Items or strategically powerful passive boosts.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/6379d5db45dfe9451d0a237fbe434115.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/50c9f190ba3057d72a4145dd4c79dff4.poster.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/50c9f190ba3057d72a4145dd4c79dff4.webm?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/50c9f190ba3057d72a4145dd4c79dff4.mp4?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Encounter Brats & Minibosses associated to their Map Level themes, which are Park, Water, Urban, and Spooky.<br></li><li> Switch up your strategies as Brats of each theme have their own common traits (e.g. status effect immunities)!<br></li><li> Progress to new Map Levels by defeating the final Big Boss unique to each Map.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/ae7e18591b6731493c57fdf3720f5d3b.poster.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/ae7e18591b6731493c57fdf3720f5d3b.webm?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/ae7e18591b6731493c57fdf3720f5d3b.mp4?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/5426c82972a452924ad2bf0523c9123a.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/110521bdb246b2f4c517fb47c862d5af.poster.avif?t=1733891696\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/110521bdb246b2f4c517fb47c862d5af.webm?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2491080/extras/110521bdb246b2f4c517fb47c862d5af.mp4?t=1733891696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Purchase PermaPerks to unlock new Perk Rewards or Permanent Buffs for your future runs.<br></li><li> Build stronger Forts with various abilities and Defend them in style with Player customization.</li></ul>",
